{"tid":1061070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ Fb遭刑事調查 涉允合作夥伴接觸用戶資訊","createTime":"2019-03-14T06:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T08:06:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36e2dce49c30bf2ec327e7f2e889e985b115430e","tid":1061070,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"社交媒體巨擘Facebook(fb)據報被紐約監管部門刑事調查。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，美國聯邦檢察官正對fb和企業的數據合作進行刑事調查。據悉，紐約檢察官發出傳票，要求最少兩間曾經與fb合作的智能手機生產商提供資料，以調查fb容許合作夥伴，接觸數以億計用戶的朋友和聯絡方法等資訊有否違法。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有內部文檔和採訪紀錄顯示，多年來fb向亞馬遜、蘋果、微軟和索尼(Sony)等全球150多家大企業提供其用戶個人數據，所涉及內容遠比fb之前披露的要多。<br />\n<br />\nfb回應稱，會與監管部門合作，認真對待事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2081003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2081003&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=db4e52aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2081003</a>"},{"pid":"bc5a94b9697dcadd37743b35f80494b490ecb64b","tid":1061070,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"原來俾人熄機調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af07356783b259304218f1bab653a5290e180bb5","tid":1061070,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}